title: Blind Man's Colour - Treats from the Garage (2008)
description:
This album was posted as a free download at blindmanscolour.blogspot .com/2008/10/rainbow-faces.html (remove the space; piratebay doesn't allow links to blogspot). I made a torrent for it because some of the DDL links from Blind Man's Colour's blog have expired, this is one of my favorite albums, and I want to have magnet links for everything I post at my blog (2kl8ancowavemp3failblog.blogspot .com).

The original download from the blog includes 7 128 kb/s MP3 files and 3 128 kb/s AAC files, but I re-encoded the AAC files as V1 MP3 because piratebay doesn't allow music torrents to contain m4a files.
